story.name: SUT::batchQueryByIdAndType()
story.description: ---@REQ: batchQueryByIdAndType if (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) then ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/BadRequestError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::BadRequestError else if (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::EMPTY) then ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/ContentLengthRequired self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::ContentLengthRequired else if (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_ERROR_HEADER or IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_TEXT_HEADER) then ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/UnsupportedMediaType self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::UnsupportedMediaType else if (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_ERROR_HEADER or IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_TEXT_HEADER) then ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/NotAcceptableMIMEtype self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::NotAcceptableMIMEtype else if (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::JSON_ERROR) then ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/ParseError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::ParseError else -- not (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) and (not (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::EMPTY) and ((not (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_ERROR_HEADER) and not (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_TEXT_HEADER)) and ((not (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_ERROR_HEADER) and not (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_TEXT_HEADER)) and not (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::JSON_ERROR)))) ---@AIM: batchQueryByIdAndType/Success let entity: Entity = Entity.allInstances()->any(e: Entity | (e.sUT.oclIsUndefined() = false and e.id = IN_ENTITYID) and e.type = IN_ENTITY_TYPE ) in self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::GET_SUCCESS endif endif endif endif endif and result = self.messageToReturn and self.checkReturnedMessage()

story.name: SUT::updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID()
story.description: ---@REQ: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID let entity: Entity = Entity.allInstances()->any(e: Entity | e.id = IN_ENTITYID ), message: RETURNED_MESSAGES = self.getAttributeDataByEntityID(URL::VALID_URL, HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_JSON_HEADER, entity.id, IN_ATTRIBUTE_NAME) in if (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) then ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/BadRequestError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::BadRequestError else if (IN_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE = ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE::EMPTY) then -- not (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) and IN_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE = ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE::EMPTY ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/ContentLengthRequired self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::ContentLengthRequired else if (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_ERROR_HEADER) then ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/UnsupportedMediaType self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::UnsupportedMediaType else if (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_JSON_HEADER) then if (message = RETURNED_MESSAGES::NotFound) then ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/NotFound self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::NotFound else if (IN_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE = ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_PAYLOAD_TYPE::JSON) then ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/Success self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::UPDATE_SUCCESS else ---@AIM: updateJsonAttributeValueByEntityID/BadRequestError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::BadRequestError endif endif endif endif endif endif and result = self.messageToReturn and self.checkReturnedMessage()

story.name: SUT::batchQueryById()
story.description: ---@REQ: batchQueryById if (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) then ---@AIM: batchQueryById/BadRequestError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::BadRequestError else if (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::EMPTY) then ---@AIM: batchQueryById/ContentLengthRequired self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::ContentLengthRequired else if (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_ERROR_HEADER or IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_TEXT_HEADER) then ---@AIM: batchQueryById/UnsupportedMediaType self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::UnsupportedMediaType else if (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_ERROR_HEADER or IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_TEXT_HEADER) then ---@AIM: batchQueryById/NotAcceptableMIMEtype self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::NotAcceptableMIMEtype else if (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::JSON_ERROR) then ---@AIM: batchQueryById/ParseError self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::ParseError else -- not (IN_URL = URL::INVALID_URL) and (not (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::EMPTY) and ((not (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_ERROR_HEADER) and not (IN_HEADERS_PAYLOAD = HEADERS_PAYLOAD::CONTENT_TYPE_TEXT_HEADER)) and ((not (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_ERROR_HEADER) and not (IN_HEADERS_RESPONSE = HEADERS_RESPONSE::ACCEPT_TEXT_HEADER)) and not (IN_BATCH_PAYLOAD = PAYLOAD::JSON_ERROR)))) ---@AIM: batchQueryById/Success let entity: Entity = Entity.allInstances()->any(e: Entity | e.sUT.oclIsUndefined() = false and e.id = IN_ENTITYID ) in self.messageToReturn = RETURNED_MESSAGES::GET_SUCCESS endif endif endif endif endif and result = self.messageToReturn and self.checkReturnedMessage()

story.name: SUT::batchUpdate()
